title: Week 11 Waivers + Full Stream Ahead, Deeeeeebo! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/16
description:
Week 11 Waiver Wire! The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Week 11 waiver pickups and QB streamers! Plus, players to consider dropping, injury updates, and a new edition of “Where There’s Smoke, There’s Fire!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 16th, 2021.
 (04:35) - Monday Night Recap: Rams at 49ers
 (11:30) - Where There’s Smoke, There’s Fire

 (28:40) - WR Waivers
 (39:50) - RB Waivers
 (51:00) - TE Waivers
